[ 26603] By: nicholas                              on 2006/01/03  15:32:38
        Log: Integrate:
             [ 25365]
             Subject: [PATCH blead] Make t/op/local.t use test.pl.
             From: Rick Delaney <rick@bort.ca>
             Date: Wed, 7 Sep 2005 22:45:44 -0400
             Message-ID: <20050908024544.GA4058@localhost.localdomain>
             
             [ 25515]
             Subject: [PATCH blead] Re: [perl #36733] %SIG not properly local-ized
             From: Rick Delaney <rick@bort.ca>
             Date: Thu, 8 Sep 2005 08:55:16 -0400
             Message-ID: <20050908125516.GA18184@localhost.localdomain>
             
             [ 25752]
